      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;block-icon-container&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;block-icon-image&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;picture&gt;&#xA;        &lt;source srcset=&#34;https://mplab-blockset.github.io/MPLAB-Device-Blocks-for-Simulink/images/blocks/block_C_Function_Call.svg&#34; type=&#34;image/svg+xml&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;img src=&#34;https://mplab-blockset.github.io/MPLAB-Device-Blocks-for-Simulink/images/blocks/block_C_Function_Call.png&#34; alt=&#34;C Function Call Block Icon&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/picture&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;block-icon-description&#34;&gt;&#xA;        Interface to custom C functions from Simulink models, enabling integration of legacy code, vendor libraries, and optimized routines with automatic code generation.&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;When to use:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;When to use:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Integrating legacy C code or existing libraries into Simulink model&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Hand-optimized assembly or C routines needed for performance-critical sections&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Vendor SDKs or third-party libraries required (CAN stacks, sensor drivers)&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Compiler built-ins needed (&lt;code&gt;__delay_ms()&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;__builtin_dmaoffset()&lt;/code&gt;, etc.)&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Custom peripheral register access not available in standard MCHP blocks&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;When NOT to use:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
